290
00:12:12,560 --> 00:12:13,240
No need.

291
00:12:13,360 --> 00:12:15,080
We are here today to accompany our eldest brother.

292
00:12:15,080 --> 00:12:16,740
He just wants to see his lover.

293
00:12:18,040 --> 00:12:19,160
Sir,

294
00:12:19,160 --> 00:12:20,360
I didn't expect

295
00:12:20,360 --> 00:12:21,800
