296
00:12:24,840 --> 00:12:26,600
I wonder which girl

297
00:12:26,600 --> 00:12:27,880
is so lucky.

298
00:12:29,640 --> 00:12:31,320
It's one of your courtesans,

299
00:12:31,320 --> 00:12:32,480
Miss Qiaoyun.

300
00:12:33,440 --> 00:12:34,880
So that's who it is.

301
00:12:35,320 --> 00:12:36,800
With Qiaoyun's looks,

302
00:12:36,800 --> 00:12:37,800
she isn't even considered average

303
00:12:37,800 --> 00:12:39,480
around here.

304
00:12:39,880 --> 00:12:40,600
How about

305
00:12:40,800 --> 00:12:42,640
I find you someone

306
00:12:42,640 --> 00:12:44,560
younger and prettier?

307
00:12:45,600 --> 00:12:46,200
No, no, no.

308
00:12:46,400 --> 00:12:47,360
My brother

309
00:12:47,360 --> 00:12:49,600
only has eyes for Miss Qiaoyun.

310
00:12:49,920 --> 00:12:52,520
Please let her know we're here.

311
00:12:53,080 --> 00:12:54,760
Unfortunately,

312
00:12:54,800 --> 00:12:56,320
Qiaoyun has been booked by someone else.

313
00:12:56,320 --> 00:12:57,680
Please come back next time.

314
00:12:57,680 --> 00:12:58,200
Next time, I...

315
00:12:58,200 --> 00:12:58,930
Impossible!

316
00:12:59,000 --> 00:13:01,400
Qiaoyun only performs, she doesn't sell her body.

317
00:13:01,400 --> 00:13:02,000
Brother.

318
00:13:02,000 --> 00:13:02,600
Forget it.

319
00:13:03,200 --> 00:13:04,160
Sir,

320
00:13:04,360 --> 00:13:05,960
as long as the price is right,

321
00:13:06,000 --> 00:13:07,080
our girls will sell anything.

322
00:13:07,080 --> 00:13:08,000
Nonsense!

323
00:13:08,080 --> 00:13:10,010
Qiaoyun isn't that kind of person.

324
00:13:10,200 --> 00:13:12,200
When I was with Qiaoyun before,

325
00:13:12,480 --> 00:13:14,800
we just drank, listened to music, wrote poetry,

326
00:13:14,800 --> 00:13:16,260
and talked about romance.

327
00:13:16,320 --> 00:13:18,450
We never did anything inappropriate.

328
00:13:18,720 --> 00:13:19,840
What, Brother?

329
00:13:20,280 --> 00:13:22,080
Writing poetry and talking about romance?

330
00:13:22,080 --> 00:13:23,760
Aren't you illiterate, Brother?

331
00:13:23,760 --> 00:13:24,480
Brother.

332
00:13:24,520 --> 00:13:25,960
Is it possible that

333
00:13:25,960 --> 00:13:28,820
she only performs for you without selling her body?

334
00:13:32,880 --> 00:13:33,400
Sir,

335
00:13:33,400 --> 00:13:34,120
calm down.

336
00:13:34,120 --> 00:13:35,160
I'll go find her for you.

337
00:13:35,160 --> 00:13:36,160
Right away.

338
00:13:53,000 --> 00:13:56,080
The mortal world weaves a cocoon.

339
00:13:56,160 --> 00:13:56,800
Yaoniang.

340
00:13:57,000 --> 00:14:00,120
Half a life of absurdity ground into sand.

341
00:14:00,680 --> 00:14:03,410
Lust is but the trace of snow on an empty mountain.

342
00:14:03,960 --> 00:14:08,080
Wealth is like a passing mirage.

343
00:14:08,200 --> 00:14:09,040
Great poem!

344
00:14:09,040 --> 00:14:09,680
Great!

345
00:14:09,880 --> 00:14:10,800
Bravo!

346
00:14:11,400 --> 00:14:12,080
Good. Good poem.

347
00:14:12,080 --> 00:14:13,080
Good poem.

348
00:14:13,240 --> 00:14:14,240
Really good.

349
00:14:15,320 --> 00:14:17,380
You have great literary talent, sir.

350
00:14:18,360 --> 00:14:20,160
You are handsome,

351
00:14:20,240 --> 00:14:21,560
free-spirited,

352
00:14:21,720 --> 00:14:23,000
and highly talented.

353
00:14:23,560 --> 00:14:25,820
But you still have to pay the brothel fee.

354
00:14:27,040 --> 00:14:28,520
You're being tacky, my lady.

355
00:14:28,520 --> 00:14:31,160
I have long since achieved enlightenment.

356
00:14:31,600 --> 00:14:34,640
The flesh is but a leaking wine skin.

357
00:14:35,000 --> 00:14:38,000
And the seven emotions are but stale wine.

358
00:14:39,160 --> 00:14:40,440
Fill it up.

359
00:14:46,120 --> 00:14:47,600
So you just don't have money, right?

360
00:14:47,600 --> 00:14:48,260
Beat him up!

361
00:14:49,280 --> 00:14:50,120
Not the face!

362
00:14:52,600 --> 00:14:54,520
Finally, I can study it properly.

363
00:14:55,720 --> 00:14:56,520
Cheat.

364
00:14:58,360 --> 00:14:59,620
How do I use this thing?

365
00:15:00,840 --> 00:15:01,560
Hint:

366
00:15:01,560 --> 00:15:02,560
Rule-type item.

367
00:15:02,560 --> 00:15:03,760
Parchment Title Deed.

368
00:15:03,760 --> 00:15:04,520
This item

369
00:15:04,520 --> 00:15:07,000
has the function to modify the rules of an area.

370
00:15:07,000 --> 00:15:08,480
As long as you are in the area,

371
00:15:08,480 --> 00:15:09,560
and write in the deed

372
00:15:09,560 --> 00:15:11,000
