373
00:15:11,080 --> 00:15:12,400
and the name of the owner,

374
00:15:12,400 --> 00:15:14,600
you can redefine the rules of the area.

375
00:15:14,760 --> 00:15:17,120
The owner can also ignore the rules,

376
00:15:17,120 --> 00:15:18,160
without any restrictions.

377
00:15:18,160 --> 00:15:19,280
Duration:

378
00:15:19,280 --> 00:15:20,160
One hour.

379
00:15:20,160 --> 00:15:21,160
Cooldown:

380
00:15:21,160 --> 00:15:22,040
Twenty-four hours.

381
00:15:22,040 --> 00:15:23,600
What a good thing.

382
00:15:23,600 --> 00:15:24,240
Note:

383
00:15:24,320 --> 00:15:27,000
If the location already belongs to the parchment owner,

384
00:15:27,000 --> 00:15:28,440
there is no time limit.

385
00:15:28,560 --> 00:15:30,960
It takes effect as long as the owner is in the area.

386
00:15:30,960 --> 00:15:31,800
Wow,

387
00:15:32,400 --> 00:15:33,880
this is so awesome!

388
00:15:34,080 --> 00:15:35,280
Let's see if it works.

389
00:15:45,160 --> 00:15:46,720
Who should I test it on?

390
00:15:47,400 --> 00:15:48,840
Han Xiaoying.

391
00:15:50,360 --> 00:15:51,720
No, no, no.

392
00:15:52,160 --> 00:15:54,040
She doesn't know what's going on right now.

393
00:15:54,040 --> 00:15:55,840
It's better to keep my distance.

394
00:15:56,960 --> 00:15:58,820
I'll just test it on the servants.

395
00:15:59,840 --> 00:16:01,080
Whoever slacks off

396
00:16:01,080 --> 00:16:02,160
and is lazy

397
00:16:02,560 --> 00:16:04,040
