399
00:16:10,520 --> 00:16:11,520
You, go mop the floor.

400
00:16:11,520 --> 00:16:12,200
Okay.

401
00:16:12,360 --> 00:16:13,320
You, go chop the wood.

402
00:16:13,320 --> 00:16:13,880
Got it.

403
00:16:13,880 --> 00:16:14,880
You, go prune the branches.

404
00:16:14,880 --> 00:16:15,540
Sure thing.

405
00:16:15,720 --> 00:16:17,180
I'll go clean the latrine.

406
00:16:19,560 --> 00:16:21,840
What kind of new gadget did you get this time?

407
00:16:21,840 --> 00:16:22,640
It's amazing.

408
00:16:23,160 --> 00:16:25,040
It can actually set rules for an area

409
00:16:25,040 --> 00:16:26,570
and alter cause and effect.

410
00:16:26,840 --> 00:16:29,480
Old man, don't be interested in everything.

411
00:16:29,680 --> 00:16:30,940
Go back to sleep early.

412
00:16:43,480 --> 00:16:44,360
It's me.

413
00:16:44,720 --> 00:16:45,720
Master.

414
00:16:47,280 --> 00:16:48,920
Your face is all bruised.

415
00:16:48,920 --> 00:16:49,780
What happened?

416
00:16:52,800 --> 00:16:54,040
This is

417
00:16:54,520 --> 00:16:56,440
