418
00:16:56,480 --> 00:16:58,360
It's the price of detoxification, right?

419
00:16:58,360 --> 00:16:58,960
You

420
00:16:59,560 --> 00:17:00,840
little brat.

421
00:17:00,840 --> 00:17:01,970
It's all your fault.

422
00:17:02,440 --> 00:17:03,520
Tell me,

423
00:17:03,880 --> 00:17:05,000
