424
00:17:05,760 --> 00:17:06,880
I was in Luoxian Town.

425
00:17:06,880 --> 00:17:08,839
I almost turned the Lin Residence upside down,

426
00:17:08,839 --> 00:17:10,680
but still couldn't find the Sha Demon Ancestor.

427
00:17:10,680 --> 00:17:11,680
I suspect

428
00:17:11,680 --> 00:17:13,210
