429
00:17:17,640 --> 00:17:18,400
Disciple.

430
00:17:18,839 --> 00:17:21,800
Are you really going to go against your eldest brother?

431
00:17:21,800 --> 00:17:23,640
You didn't want to fight with him before.

432
00:17:23,640 --> 00:17:25,960
Coming here to catch some little demons was harmless.

433
00:17:25,960 --> 00:17:26,920
But the Sha Demon Ancestor,

434
00:17:26,920 --> 00:17:28,400
