440
00:17:38,920 --> 00:17:40,520
If he were to become the emperor,

441
00:17:40,520 --> 00:17:42,440
what would become of this world?

442
00:17:42,440 --> 00:17:43,480
What becomes of the world

443
00:17:43,480 --> 00:17:44,880
