444
00:17:45,080 --> 00:17:46,680
You are my disciple.

445
00:17:46,680 --> 00:17:47,920
I can't let anything happen to you.

446
00:17:47,920 --> 00:17:48,920
Come back with me.

447
00:17:49,160 --> 00:17:49,920
Master.

448
00:17:50,640 --> 00:17:51,720
This time,

449
00:17:51,960 --> 00:17:53,360
